In the Netherlands it’s:

Base(8 years, starting at around 4 years of age)
Secondary(roughly 4 levels, 4/5 years)
Optional: Higher education(about 4 years)

Depending on what difficulty/profession you pick, you go to school from age 5-17 to 5-22.
